local loaded=false function AntiAFK()if loaded then return end loaded=true local Players=game:GetService("Players")local UIS=game:GetService("UserInputService")local TweenService=game:GetService("TweenService")local lp=Players.LocalPlayer local function getRandomInterval()return 25+math.random()*20 end local gui=Instance.new("ScreenGui")gui.Parent=game.CoreGui gui.IgnoreGuiInset=true gui.ZIndexBehavior=Enum.ZIndexBehavior.Sibling local tip=Instance.new("TextLabel")tip.Size=UDim2.new(0,320,0,70)tip.Position=UDim2.new(0.5,0,0.5,0)tip.AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(0.5,0.5)tip.Text="防挂机已启动"tip.TextColor3=Color3.fromRGB(0,255,128)tip.BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(0,0,0)tip.BackgroundTransparency=0.3 tip.Font=Enum.Font.GothamBold tip.TextSize=32 tip.TextStrokeTransparency=0 tip.TextStrokeColor3=Color3.new(0,0,0)tip.ZIndex=999 tip.Parent=gui Instance.new("UICorner",tip).CornerRadius=UDim.new(0,12)tip.BackgroundTransparency=1 tip.TextTransparency=1 local inTween=TweenService:Create(tip,TweenInfo.new(0.4),{BackgroundTransparency=0.3,TextTransparency=0})local outTween=TweenService:Create(tip,TweenInfo.new(0.6),{BackgroundTransparency=1,TextTransparency=1})inTween:Play()task.delay(5,function()outTween:Play()outTween.Completed:Wait()tip:Destroy()end)local statusDot=Instance.new("Frame")statusDot.Size=UDim2.new(0,12,0,12)statusDot.Position=UDim2.new(1,-20,1,-20)statusDot.AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(1,1)statusDot.BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(0,255,128)statusDot.BackgroundTransparency=0.3 statusDot.ZIndex=999 statusDot.Parent=gui Instance.new("UICorner",statusDot).CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0)task.spawn(function()while gui.Parent do for i=0.3,0.9,0.05 do statusDot.BackgroundTransparency=i task.wait(0.03)end for i=0.9,0.3,-0.05 do statusDot.BackgroundTransparency=i task.wait(0.03)end end end)local function getValidCharacter()local char=lp.Character if not char then return nil,nil,nil end local hum=char:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid")local root=char:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart")if not root or not hum or hum.Health<=0 then return nil,nil,nil end if hum:GetState()==Enum.HumanoidStateType.Dead then return nil,nil,nil end return char,hum,root end local function actionWalk()local char,hum,root=getValidCharacter()if not char then return end local moveDir=Vector3.new((math.random()-0.5)*2,0,(math.random()-0.5)*2).Unit*0.5 hum:Move(moveDir,false)task.wait(0.2+math.random()*0.3)hum:Move(Vector3.zero,false)end local function actionJump()local char,hum,root=getValidCharacter()if not char then return end hum.Jump=true task.wait(0.1)end local function actionLook()local char,hum,root=getValidCharacter()if not char then return end workspace.CurrentCamera.CFrame*=CFrame.Angles(math.rad((math.random()-0.5)*0.3),math.rad((math.random()-0.5)*0.5),0)end local function actionKeyPress()local char,hum,root=getValidCharacter()if not char then return end local keys={Enum.KeyCode.W,Enum.KeyCode.A,Enum.KeyCode.S,Enum.KeyCode.D}local key=keys[math.random(1,#keys)]UIS:FireKey(key,true)task.wait(0.05+math.random()*0.1)UIS:FireKey(key,false)end local function DoAFK()local actionCount=1+math.random(0,2)local actions={actionWalk,actionJump,actionLook,actionKeyPress}for i=1,actionCount do actions[math.random(1,#actions)]()task.wait(0.1+math.random()*0.3)end end task.spawn(function()while task.wait(getRandomInterval())do DoAFK()end end)end AntiAFK()